# Advanced Filters

Take photos with filter effects.

1. Rotate the drive dial to **ADV**.

   !Drive Dial

2. Navigate to **DRIVE SETTING > ADV. FILTER SETTING** in the !Shooting Setting Icon **SHOOTING SETTING** menu and choose a filter effect.
